00:39:26.530 --> 00:39:28.650
So, that's the answer to the poetry.

00:39:28.650 --> 00:39:29.483
- It's interesting here

00:39:29.483 --> 00:39:32.530
because of the textual
analysis you're doing

00:39:32.530 --> 00:39:36.170
and the work of your scholarship.

