00:42:07.350 --> 00:42:09.190
on American politics.

00:42:09.190 --> 00:42:14.190
And here we're talking
about the apocalyptic vision

00:42:14.540 --> 00:42:17.500
to solve this problem,
to explain suffering

00:42:17.500 --> 00:42:19.080
by the notion of apocalypse.

00:42:19.080 --> 00:42:23.550
And your analysis points to the way

00:42:23.550 --> 00:42:28.550
that this appears initially
in the Old Testament,

00:42:30.460 --> 00:42:32.523
in the Book of Daniel.

00:42:33.460 --> 00:42:34.780
Talk a little about that,

00:42:34.780 --> 00:42:36.680
and then help us understand

00:42:36.680 --> 00:42:40.290
what the key components
were to this answer.

00:42:40.290 --> 00:42:45.270
- Yeah, this answer becomes
prominent in early Judaism,

00:42:47.350 --> 00:42:50.384
near the end of the Hebrew Bible period

00:42:50.384 --> 00:42:51.570
in the Book of Daniel,

00:42:51.570 --> 00:42:53.630
which is the last of the
books of the Hebrew Bible--

00:42:53.630 --> 00:42:55.620
- And that would have been
what year the hundred uh--

00:42:55.620 --> 00:42:58.070
- About 150, 160 BCE.

00:42:58.070 --> 00:43:02.660
So, but this view becomes
dominant in the New Testament

00:43:02.660 --> 00:43:07.463
and becomes the explanatory
position of the New Testament.

00:43:11.770 --> 00:43:13.350
This view is called apocalyptic

00:43:13.350 --> 00:43:16.410
because it's based on the
Greek word apokalupsis

00:43:16.410 --> 00:43:19.540
which means revealing or an unveiling.

00:43:19.540 --> 00:43:22.900
The idea is that God has
revealed the heavenly secrets

00:43:22.900 --> 00:43:25.090
that can make sense of earthly realities,

00:43:25.090 --> 00:43:29.690
and so God explains why this
world is in the state it's in.

00:43:29.690 --> 00:43:31.450
The apocalypticists were reacting

00:43:31.450 --> 00:43:33.860
against the prophetic point of view.

00:43:33.860 --> 00:43:36.400
The prophets thought that
God was punishing people,

00:43:36.400 --> 00:43:38.140
that's why they were suffering.

00:43:38.140 --> 00:43:41.010
But the apocalypticists realized
that righteous people are

00:43:41.010 --> 00:43:42.070
the ones who are suffering,

00:43:42.070 --> 00:43:43.880
and so God must not be punishing them.

00:43:43.880 --> 00:43:45.230
So, why are they suffering?

00:43:45.230 --> 00:43:47.400
And the apocalypticists
came up with the idea

00:43:47.400 --> 00:43:49.690
that there are forces opposed to God

00:43:49.690 --> 00:43:51.830
that are creating suffering in the world.

00:43:51.830 --> 00:43:54.610
This is the period in
which Jewish thinkers came

00:43:54.610 --> 00:43:57.270
to think that God has a
personal enemy, the Devil.

00:43:57.270 --> 00:43:59.500
And the Devil has demons who work

00:43:59.500 --> 00:44:02.040
his nefarious ways here on earth,

00:44:02.040 --> 00:44:04.030
and there're all these cosmic forces

00:44:04.030 --> 00:44:06.670
that are creating havoc here on earth.

00:44:06.670 --> 00:44:10.630
But God is ultimately going
to establish his sovereignty

00:44:10.630 --> 00:44:13.390
over the world by destroying
these forces of evil

00:44:13.390 --> 00:44:16.070
and setting up a good kingdom on earth.

00:44:16.070 --> 00:44:19.090
And so, the apocalypticists
believed that in the future

00:44:19.090 --> 00:44:21.340
God would once again reassert himself

00:44:21.340 --> 00:44:23.650
and good would emerge triumphant,

00:44:23.650 --> 00:44:26.090
and God's Kingdom would come to replace

00:44:26.090 --> 00:44:28.340
these wicked earthly kingdoms on earth.

00:44:28.340 --> 00:44:31.650
- Now when you're discussing
