00:44:31.650 --> 00:44:36.467
it becomes very interesting
that his prophecies

00:44:37.650 --> 00:44:42.650
and descriptions come at a
time when the Greek influence,

00:44:45.580 --> 00:44:48.750
and the efforts by the
Greek Empire at that time,

00:44:48.750 --> 00:44:53.750
to Hellenize and to stop the
