00:45:09.980 --> 00:45:12.380
which is celebrated by Jews today

00:45:12.380 --> 00:45:14.683
as the holiday of Hanukkah.

00:45:16.807 --> 00:45:20.600
So, Daniel is a man of his time

00:45:20.600 --> 00:45:25.600
who's dealing with real historical forces,

00:45:26.130 --> 00:45:31.130
the efforts to colonize this
Jewish community in Judea,

00:45:35.810 --> 00:45:40.810
and his language becomes
very metaphorical, basically.

00:45:41.270 --> 00:45:42.230
- Yeah, that's right.

00:45:42.230 --> 00:45:44.940
So, this was an awful time period

00:45:44.940 --> 00:45:46.563
for people living in Israel.

00:45:47.487 --> 00:45:50.810
The monarch of Syria, who
was trying to Hellenize,

00:45:50.810 --> 00:45:54.420
trying to make Israel Greek,

00:45:54.420 --> 00:45:58.380
basically outlawed the
possibility of following Torah,

00:45:58.380 --> 00:46:00.360
so that to the extent

00:46:00.360 --> 00:46:03.630
that women who had their
baby boy circumcised,

00:46:03.630 --> 00:46:06.150
the children would be murdered

00:46:06.150 --> 00:46:08.030
and hanged around their mothers' necks.

00:46:08.030 --> 00:46:10.374
And we learned about this
in some of these books

00:46:10.374 --> 00:46:13.870
of First and Second
Maccabees, for example.

00:46:13.870 --> 00:46:15.560
And Daniel is responding to this.

00:46:15.560 --> 00:46:18.550
He sees this not just as human evil,

00:46:18.550 --> 00:46:19.620
bad things that humans do,

00:46:19.620 --> 00:46:23.100
he sees it in a bigger
cosmic context that, in fact,

00:46:23.100 --> 00:46:25.220
there are forces that are bigger than us

00:46:25.220 --> 00:46:26.410
that are at work in this world

00:46:26.410 --> 00:46:28.690
that are creating this kind of havoc.

00:46:28.690 --> 00:46:31.420
And since these are cosmic forces,

00:46:31.420 --> 00:46:33.700
they need to be dealt
with on the cosmic level.

00:46:33.700 --> 00:46:35.830
God himself is going to intervene

00:46:35.830 --> 00:46:38.340
and destroy these forces of evil,

00:46:38.340 --> 00:46:40.210
and get rid of the evil kingdoms

00:46:40.210 --> 00:46:42.310
to set up his good kingdom on earth.

00:46:42.310 --> 00:46:45.490
- Now and you suggest that when you look

00:46:45.490 --> 00:46:46.733
at what they're writing,

00:46:46.733 --> 00:46:50.990
it's on the one hand very descriptive,

00:46:50.990 --> 00:46:54.910
it's like four chapters have been written

00:46:54.910 --> 00:46:57.080
and these are the chapters of where we are

00:46:57.080 --> 00:46:58.830
and what has happened to us, and so on.

00:46:58.830 --> 00:47:03.830
And that what the
apocalypticists are giving

