00:47:07.370 --> 00:47:09.590
looking ahead to the future.

00:47:09.590 --> 00:47:13.210
So, in a way, they're
kind of futurologists.

00:47:13.210 --> 00:47:14.400
- Yes, absolutely, in fact,

00:47:14.400 --> 00:47:16.860
