is recounting what's already
happened in the past.

00:47:41.420 --> 00:47:43.470
So that the reader reads this

00:47:43.470 --> 00:47:46.140
and thinks that this
ancient person was correct

00:47:46.140 --> 00:47:48.130
about all of his predictions.

00:47:48.130 --> 00:47:50.110
But the author then goes on to predict

00:47:50.110 --> 00:47:51.570
what's going to happen next,

00:47:51.570 --> 00:47:54.600
and the reader doesn't realize
that now he's changed gears

00:47:54.600 --> 00:47:57.820
and is talking about what's
going to happen in the future.

00:47:57.820 --> 00:48:00.110
The reader thinks the whole
thing has been a prediction,

00:48:00.110 --> 00:48:03.700
but this then provides
validation for his predictions

00:48:03.700 --> 00:48:05.660
